### Go profile

| Step      | Check                                                     | Fix                        | Gate                                       |
|-----------|-----------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| goimports | `output=$(goimports -l {{ files }}) && test -z "$output"` | `goimports -w {{ files }}` | `**/*.go`; all hooks                       |
| gofumpt   | `output=$(gofumpt -l {{ files }}) && test -z "$output"`   | `gofumpt -w {{ files }}`   | `**/*.go`; after goimports; all hooks      |
| modules   | `go mod tidy -diff && go mod verify`                      | `go mod tidy`              | root `go.mod`; check/fix; never pre-commit |
| lint      | `golangci-lint run`                                       | none                       | root `go.mod`; check only                  |
| tests     | `go test ./...`                                           | none                       | root `go.mod`; check only                  |

The mise-managed tools are `go`, `gofumpt`, `go:golang.org/x/tools/cmd/goimports`, and `golangci-lint`, all at `latest`.
The profile ignores `coverage.out`.

