| Step    | Check                                       | Fix                      | Gate                                            |
|---------|---------------------------------------------|--------------------------|-------------------------------------------------|
| format  | `mix format --check-formatted {{ files }}`  | `mix format {{ files }}` | `**/*.{ex,exs}`; all hooks                      |
